Animations

    - this is basically a more powerful transition
    




    animation-name
        - a css property for declaring a given selection has an animation
    animation-duration
        - a css property for declaring the length of a given animation
    animation-fill-mode
        - dictates how an animation will behave on completion
        options:
            - forwards : locks the animation at the 100% mark
    animation-iteration-count
        - specifies how many animation you want to occur
        options:
            - number - loops animation number times
            - infinite - allows the animation to loop indefinitely